I still find it unbelievable that an monster that can only travel on the ground, could have conquered Earth. Unless some unseen flying monster is a thing, or if it gets revealed that the monsters are smaller versions of some Cthulhu type Kaiju monster. All the military would need to do is engage them with attack helicopters only. Or if the attack was underway, our technology is close enough we could develop Exo-Suits to defend against the monsters claws.


Just look up the new metal in military applications "super magnesium metal alloy". It can take a .50 Barrett (armor piercing round) at 5 ft away without denting. That's Star Trek starship type strength!
